*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form cal_date
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM cal_date USING VALUE(p_date)
                    VALUE(p_days)
              CHANGING VALUE(p_new_date).
"gv_a = sy-datum + 7.
"gv_a = p_date + 7.
p_new_date = p_date + p_days.

ENDFORM.

FORM display_info .
WRITE: gv_a, gv_b, gv_c, gv_d.            "글로벌 변수이므로 sub-routine과 상단에서도 쓸 수 있다.

ENDFORM.

*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form cal_date2w
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM cal_date2w USING VALUE(p_date)
                      VALUE(p_days)
                CHANGING VALUE(p_new_date).
p_new_date = p_date + p_days.
ENDFORM.

